ouse to select multiple addresses in the breakpoints section doesn't behave properly; rather than highlighting multiple entries, it toggles the current breakpoint. Shift with the arrow keys works correctly, however.<br />- The &quot;Bring debugger to front on break&quot; option unexpectedly applies to loading saved states.</div>

